{"tid":1091620,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友中意著底胸背心 向各路絲打求教防走光秘訣","createTime":"2019-04-04T09:05:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T10:14:34.000Z","uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"45dd13ce670092c628242831d30861b6e6badf07","tid":1091620,"uid":216268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T09:05:23.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打，夏日將至 又係著吊帶背心嘅好日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作為男友嘅我當然唔想佢走光 但佢都係堅持要唔戴bra著背心 尼家求救各路巴絲有冇咩防走光嘅技巧傳授小弟 等我有一兩招防身<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔單止係背心，短裙各類都係呀總之有機會走光嘅都求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc9cbb49f1b60b0f1a790b2084d622bd3c450343","tid":1091620,"uid":111460,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.wikia.com/evchk/images/7/76/Chan100pic.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.wikia.com%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F7%2F76%2FChan100pic.jpg&h=e0cf667b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b74d5446e747969271574dcf8c900432c764261","tid":1091620,"uid":431,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T09:08:02.000Z","msg":"平胸先會走光"},{"pid":"f54c3bf08461d160ccaefbdef631b5c3595eaa03","tid":1091620,"uid":225347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T09:34:24.000Z","msg":"算吧啦，咁樣著得就係想俾靚仔望佢走光，俾任何建議你佢都會話戴左/用左會唔舒服"},{"pid":"971da6df1c6e17f38b31ad653bcacd0e2ca03435","tid":1091620,"uid":125992,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T10:03:56.000Z","msg":"男人老狗着背心都怕走光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e23d37d12745abe25c85e2f7b9c9110580865af","tid":1091620,"uid":36894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T10:14:34.000Z","msg":"有冇人順便教埋佢中文？"}]}